To run the service locally:

$ python3 -m http.server 8000


Chrome Web Store
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

$ zip -r conversai.zip manifest.json background.js content.js db.js icons

Then publish

Go to the Chrome Web Store Developer Dashboard.

Add new item -  upload conversai.zip.

Fill listing details (name - ConversAI -, descriptions, screenshots, privacy policy URL).

Submit for review.

Quick privacy policy template (paste on your site)

ConversAI Privacy Policy (Browser Extension)

ConversAI processes and stores your chat content locally in your
browser to provide search across ChatGPT, Claude, and
Gemini. ConversAI does not collect, transmit, or sell your chat
content to our servers or third parties. You can pause capture or
delete all locally stored data at any time via the extension
settings. If you enable an optional sync/backup feature in the future,
any data would be encrypted client-side before leaving your device.

